<li>Braun, Edward. 1982. "Stanislavsky and <a href="/wiki/Anton_Chekhov" title="Anton Chekhov">Chekhov</a>". <i>The Director and the Stage: From Naturalism to Grotowski</i>. London: Methuen. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0413463001" class="internal">ISBN 0413463001</a>. p.59-76.</li>
