<li>---. 2000. "Stanislavsky's System: Pathways for the Actor". In <i>Twentieth Century Actor Training</i>. Ed. Alison Hodge. London and New York: Routledge. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0415194520" class="internal">ISBN 0415194520</a>. p.11-36.</li>
<li>Counsell, Colin. 1996. <i>Signs of Performance: An Introduction to Twentieth-Century Theatre.</i> London and New York: Routledge. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0415106435" class="internal">ISBN 0415106435</a>.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Uta_Hagen" title="Uta Hagen">Hagen, Uta</a>. 1973. <i>Respect for Acting</i>. New York: Macmillan. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0025473905" class="internal">ISBN 0025473905</a>.</li>
