<li>---. 1961. <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Creating_a_Role&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Creating a Role (page does not exist)">Creating a Role</a>.</i> Trans. Elizabeth Reynolds Hapgood. London: Mentor, 1968. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0450001660" class="internal">ISBN 0450001660</a>.</li>
