<li>---. 1968. <i>Stanislavski's Legacy: A Collection of Comments on a Variety of Aspects of an Actor's Art and Life.</i> Ed. and trans. Elizabeth Reynolds Hapgood. Revised and expanded edition. London: Methuen, 1981. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0413477703" class="internal">ISBN 0413477703</a>.</li>
